  EffectDiscription_ENG: '[When Digivolving][On Play] Reveal the top 5 cards of your
    deck. Add 1 [Analogman] among them to your hand, and add 1 card with [Cyborg]
    or [Machine] in its traits to your hand or place it under this Digimon as its
    bottom digivolution card. Trash the rest.[On Deletion] By placing 1 of your [Analogman]s
    in play at the bottom of its owner''s deck, you may play 1 [Machinedramon] from
    your hand without paying the cost.'
